    <h2>Web Service</h2>
    <h3>Basic concept</h3>
        <p>Web service is a new kind of Web application that fits for distributed environment.</p>
        <p>Web service provides a set of interfaces to the outside world.These interfaces describes a set of operations that can be transfered by the user using standard XML message passing mechanism.</p>
        <p>Web service can be described using standard XML protocol, which is called service description of Web service. This description contains all details that are needed to interact with service, including message format (detail description operation), transfer protocol and Web service location. This interface hides details of service implementation.It allows implementation of the service by independent hardware/software platform or programming language. This allows Web service based application to become loosely coupled and component oriented implementation.</p>
        <p>Web service executes a specific task or a set of tasks. Web service implements complex business exchanged by independently or with other Web services.</p>
